Ally Financial Inc. Key Developments

Ally Financial Inc. Declares Quarterly Cash Dividend, Payable on August 15, 2017
Jul 19 17
The board of directors of Ally Financial Inc. declared a quarterly cash dividend of $0.12 per share of the company's common stock, payable on August 15, 2017 to shareholders of record on August 1, 2017.


Federal Reserve Approves Ally Financial Inc.'s Plan to Pay a Dividend for the Third Quarter of 2017
Jun 29 17
Ally Financial's capital plan was approved by the Federal Reserve during the Fed's comprehensive capital analysis and review. The plan includes a $0.04 increase in the company's quarterly dividend, and 9% increase in its share repurchase program. Accordingly, Ally will pay a $0.12 per share dividend in third quarter.


Ally Financial Inc. Presents at Morgan Stanley Financials Conference, Jun-14-2017 08:50 AM
May 13 17
Ally Financial Inc. Presents at Morgan Stanley Financials Conference, Jun-14-2017 08:50 AM. Venue: InterContinental New York Barclay Hotel, New York, New York, United States. Speakers: Bradley Brown, Corporate Treasurer, Christopher A. Halmy, Chief Financial Officer.


